high_descs: Turn left and walk forward then turn right to approach the sink
Pick up the left most knife from the left side of the sink
Move slightly left then turn back to face the counter
Cut the right most lettuce on the counter using the knife
Move a few feet back to the right to face the sink
Put the knife down in the sink
Move back left to face the counter with the lettuce on it
Pick up a piece of lettuce from the counter
Move a few feet right to face the sink
Wash the lettuce piece under water in the sink then remove it
Turn right and walk down to the end of the counter by the wall
Put the lettuce piece in the recycling bin under the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the washed lettuce piece in the recycling bin

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the stool, then turn right and go to the kitchen side of the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the tomato.
Turn left, step forward, then turn right to  see heads of lettuce on the counter.
Slice the lettuce in the back of the counter.
Turn right and return to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn left and go to the sliced lettuce.
Take the left piece of the sliced lettuce.
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink on the left.
Place the slice of lettuce to the left of the knife. Turn on the water for a few seconds then turn off and pick up the lettuce.
Turn right and go to the end of the hall, then turn left to see a recycling bin below the counter.
Place the lettuce in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Wash a slice of lettuce and place in recycling bin.

high_descs: Turn left and face the sink on your right.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the lettuce on the counter to your right.
Slice the lettuce on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink to your left.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the lettuce on the counter on your right.
Take a lettuce slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink on your left.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink in front of you then take it out.
Turn right and face the green bin on your left.
Place the lettuce slice in the bin in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean lettuce slice in the green bin.
